    "extract": "Sono 'Okodawari', Ore ni mo Kure yo! (Japanese: その『おこだわり』、俺にもくれよ!!; \"Give Me Those Fixations Too!\") is a Japanese comedy manga written and illustrated by Tōru Seino. It was published in Kodansha's Monthly Morning Two from November 2014 to October 2015. and later in Morning from December 2015 to April 2018, with its chapters collected in five wide-ban volumes.\nIt was adapted into a mockumentary television series titled Sono 'Okodawari', Watashi ni mo Kure yo!! (その『おこだわり』、私にもくれよ!!), broadcast on TV Tokyo and TV Osaka starting in April 2016."
